OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1775578269
OL,3,CThree new railway stations open to the
OL,4,Cpublic for the first time
OL,6,FThe Camp Hill railway line in South
OL,7,FBirmingham has reopened to the public
OL,8,Ffor the first time in over 80 years.
OL,10,FAs part of this, three new stations
OL,11,Fhave also opened, Moseley Village,
OL,12,FKings Heath and Pineapple Road in
OL,13,FStirchley welcome passengers this
OL,14,Fmorning.
OL,16,FThe three stations provide passengers
OL,17,Fwith a direct rail link to the city
OL,18,Fcentre.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
