OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1775578269
OL,3,CThree new railway stations open to the
OL,4,Cpublic for the first time
OL,6,FThe three new stations feature
OL,7,Fsheltered platforms, accessible lifts,
OL,8,Fpassenger help points on each platform
OL,9,Fand secure cycle racks.
OL,11,FPineapple Road and Moseley Village
OL,12,Fwill also have pick-up and drop-off
OL,13,Fareas.
OL,15,FThe first train to call at the new
OL,16,Fstations was at 6:27am this morning
OL,17,F(April 7th) from New Street to Kings
OL,18,FNorton.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
