PN,37504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1775578269
OL,3,CThree new railway stations open to the
OL,4,Cpublic for the first time
OL,6,FThe train service runs every half an
OL,7,Fhour Monday-Saturday and hourly on
OL,8,FSundays.
OL,10,FTransport for West Midlands, executive
OL,11,Fdirector Sandeep Shingadia said:
OL,12,F"These vibrant neighbourhoods of
OL,13,FMoseley, Kings Heath and Stirchley
OL,14,Fhave waited 85 years for a direct rail
OL,15,Flink to the heart of Birmingham `
OL,16,Ftoday, that has changed.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
